25:41.901 --> 25:45.085
up. And what did you do after that? Well, after 
that, after they closed up,

25:47.528 --> 25:56.680
I went to work for a fellow to move people, driving a 
truck. Moving company, huh? Mm-hmm. I worked for

25:59.062 --> 26:03.066
them two or three years, and then he got into bad 
shape. He had the TB, and he had to quit, and his wife

26:03.086 --> 26:06.989
got mad and hit him. Then I went to work for the city, 
and I worked for the city about eight years. And I

26:13.135 --> 26:14.696
got mad at them one day. That's when the alcohol 
come in here. That strip mine come in here. And I

26:21.863 --> 26:26.267
asked them for a raise. They wouldn't give me a 
raise. They wouldn't give me 75 cents an hour. So

26:31.736 --> 26:32.957
they wouldn't give me no raise. And I went to 36. I 
went to work for 37. I went to work strip mine. I'd

26:42.271 --> 26:44.495
get the alcohol where the alcohol was on. I went to 
work. I worked out there. In 36 to 48, that's when

26:47.940 --> 26:54.229
they had to close down and the alcohol come in here. 
